                     </origPlace></creation><langUsage><language ident="de-x-enh" source="http://medieval-plants.org/mps-daten/inhalt/">Bavarian</language></langUsage></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body xml:space="preserve"><div type="recipe" xml:lang="de-x-enh" n="19" xml:id="br1.19"> <opener>wild <title key="Pike, prepared in three ways">ein andern <ingredient en="northern pike" commodity="Q83363026">hecht</ingredient></title> machen</opener> So <instruction>nim in her</instruction> vnd <instruction>pach in vmb daz <ingredient commodity="Q107246654" en="northern pike head">hawpt</ingredient></instruction> <instruction>da mit sewd in ander mitt mit ainem nassen <tool en="cheesecloth" commodity="Q2621157">tuech</tool></instruction> . vnd <instruction>sewd ain <ingredient en="wine" commodity="Q282">wein</ingredient> in ainner <tool en="pan" commodity="Q127666">phan</tool></instruction> . vnd <instruction>gews in auff daz <tool en="cheesecloth" commodity="Q2621157">tuech</tool> da dw den <ingredient en="northern pike" commodity="Q83363026">fisch</ingredient> sieden wild</instruction> . <instruction>daz treib vncz er sein genueg gewinn</instruction> . vnd <instruction>leg in dan twerich auff zwen <tool en="brick" commodity="Q40089">ziegell stain</tool> alz vorr vnd er roch sey</instruction> . <instruction>nach dem <ingredient commodity="Q107304832" en="northern pike tail">zagel</ingredient> mit einem <ingredient en="flour" commodity="Q36465">melb</ingredient> alz einem andern pachen <ingredient en="fish" commodity="Q600396" ana="comparison">visch</ingredient></instruction> . vnd <instruction>nim ein haizz <ingredient en="lard" commodity="Q72827">smalcz</ingredient> in ain <tool en="pan" commodity="Q127666">phann</tool></instruction> <instruction>da mit peslach den <ingredient en="northern pike" commodity="Q83363026">visch</ingredient> vncz er sich pach</instruction> <closer>so ist er perait</closer></div></body></text></TEI>